skin.name: Nautica 05
skin.description: Design based on Nautica 05 by Studio7designs. This skin includes 2 extra header images. You can find them in the skins/nautica05/assets/images/bg directory. They are named header_image_2.jpg and header_image_3.jpg. If you want to use them, you can rename one of them to header_image.jpg and rename the current header_image.jpg to some other name. Refresh your browser (you may also need to clean your browser's cache) to see it.
skin.author: AsFusion
